column5: Copied from another website......................  Hey! It ain't easy to begin with, and then you add in fixed bayonets!  The US Navy Ceremonial Guard Drill Team was invited to compete in an International Tattoo in Norway in May of 2009. The Navy competed against military units from all over NATO and won first place. I think when you watch this video you'll see why they won.  http://www.whc.net/rjones/USN/USN_team.html
